<h2><a href="#math" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="math"></a>Math</h2>
<p>Inline math: <span data-math-style="inline">E = mc^2</span></p>
<p>Display math:</p>
<p><span data-math-style="display">
\int_{-\infty}^{\infty} e^{-x^2} dx = \sqrt{\pi}
</span></p>
<p>Code-style inline: <code data-math-style="inline">\alpha + \beta</code></p>
<p>Code-style display:</p>
<pre lang="math" data-math-style="display"><code>\sum_{i=1}^{n} i = \frac{n(n+1)}{2}
</code></pre>
<p>Mixed: The equation <span data-math-style="inline">a^2 + b^2 = c^2</span> is well known.</p>
